# ==============================================================================
# LegalLocal RAG - ChromaDB Directory
# ==============================================================================
#
# This directory is used for ChromaDB vector store persistence (optional).
#
# CURRENT CONFIGURATION: In-Memory (Ephemeral)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The application currently uses in-memory storage, meaning:
# - Vectors are lost when the application restarts
# - Each session requires re-uploading documents
# - Maximum privacy: no data persisted to disk
#
# TO ENABLE PERSISTENCE:
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Modify the create_vector_store() function in app.py:
#
# vector_store = lc["Chroma"].from_documents(
#     documents=_documents,
#     embedding=_embeddings,
#     collection_name=collection_name,
#     persist_directory=str(CHROMA_DIR)  # Add this line
# )
#
# SECURITY NOTE:
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# If using persistence with sensitive legal documents:
# 1. Encrypt this directory when not in use
# 2. Clear contents after each case/project
# 3. Include in backup/destruction procedures
#
# ==============================================================================

